<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinics-transplant-center-in-florida-performs-10000th-transplant/">Mayo Clinic&amp;#8217;s transplant center in Florida performs 10,000th transplant</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9-1024x576.jpg" alt="Photograph of a surgical setting" class="wp-image-407593" srcset="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9-300x169.jpg 300w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9-768x432.jpg 768w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Surgical_Setting_16x9.jpg 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p></p>



<p>On October 29, the Transplant Center at&amp;nbsp;<a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/patient-visitor-guide/florida" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mayo Clinic in Florida</a> performed its 10,000th transplant since the program launched in 1998. The milestone is a reflection of the lives transformed through the gift of organ donation.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="alignright size-full is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="506" height="506" src="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Dr.-Burcin-Taner-WF3982960_0039-f1-x-1.jpg" alt="Dr. Burcin Taner" class="wp-image-407645" style="width:184px;height:auto" srcset="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Dr.-Burcin-Taner-WF3982960_0039-f1-x-1.jpg 506w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Dr.-Burcin-Taner-WF3982960_0039-f1-x-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/Dr.-Burcin-Taner-WF3982960_0039-f1-x-1-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Dr. Burcin Taner</figcaption></figure></div>


<p>"Every transplant represents the work of an extraordinary team dedicated to restoring hope and health," says&amp;nbsp;<a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/biographies/taner-c-burcin-m-d/bio-20054935" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Dr. Burcin Taner</a>,&amp;nbsp;chair of the Department of Transplantation at Mayo Clinic in Florida. "Reaching this milestone reflects our clinical excellence and the trust our patients place in Mayo Clinic. Together, we're shaping the next era of transplantation — one defined by innovation, collaboration and compassion."</p>



<p>The Florida Transplant Program began as a liver transplant program. Kidney transplant was added in 2000, followed by heart and lung transplants in 2001. The transplant program reports some of the highest survival rates, the lowest median wait times and the highest volumes in the country, according to the <a href="https://www.srtr.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Scientific Registry of Transplant Recipients</a>.</p>



<p>The 10,000th transplant places the program among the top transplant centers nationwide for overall transplant volume. Additionally, the transplant center is on track for a record volume year, having performed more than 465 procedures by Oct. 29.</p>



<p>Nationally, <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/departments-centers/transplant-center/home/orc-20203891" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mayo Clinic's Transplant Center</a>, which offers transplant services at its campuses in Arizona, Florida and Minnesota, is a leader in treating patients with heart disease. Combined volumes rank Mayo Clinic first among all adult transplant centers in the nation.</p>



<p>Mayo Clinic physicians have experience treating patients with complex conditions who may need <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/departments-centers/transplant-center/multiorgan-transplants/gnc-20203913" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">multiorgan transplants</a>, including heart-lung, kidney-pancreas, heart-lung-liver transplants and more.</p>



<p>"Every transplant tells a story of teamwork, trust and commitment," Dr. Taner says. "The growing volume of transplants at Mayo Clinic is the ultimate testament that our patients value our expertise and sense the dedication behind our care."</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinics-transplant-center-in-florida-performs-10000th-transplant/">Mayo Clinic&amp;#8217;s transplant center in Florida performs 10,000th transplant</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
